name: Lost Trail Outfitters
tag_list: screen-printing, embroidery, banner-printing, business-cards, specialty-printing, graphic-design
overview: Lost Trail Outfitters is a family owned and operated Custom Printing and Graphics Company located in Las Vegas Nevada. Lost Trail offers custom screen printing, embroidery, heat press, pad printing and promotional products. Lost Trail is more than just a Screen Printer and Embroidery, they also offer other services such as banners, business cards, post cards, flyers, signs and much more. Lost Trail also offers a graphics department to help with design, logo creation or to cleanup your existing artwork. Consider Lost Trail your one stop shop for all your printing needs.
